---
title: Lemony Rainbow Trout & Cacio e Pepe Linguine with Crispy Broccoli, Burst Tomatoes, and Chilies
description: Cacio e Pepe means cheese and pepper in Italian, and usually refers to a simple pasta dish consisting of just Parmesan, salt, and freshly cracked black pepper. We’re adding trout, tender broccoli and burst tomatoes as a healthy twist to make this unbeatable pasta dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lemony-rainbow-trout-cacio-e-pep-fe3fdb7e.jpg
